{"tid":1540600,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"動議撒回不是正式撒回","createTime":"2019-09-04T11:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T12:08:40.000Z","uid":29319,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c614f49a1d880bd95d5d093ffb33afb2eac3d95b","tid":1540600,"uid":29319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:56:14.000Z","msg":"正視聽！醒啦仆街！<br />\n⛔ 只係動議撤回⛔ <br />\n⛔ 只係動議撤回⛔ <br />\n⛔ 只係動議撤回⛔ <br />\n出口術咋，未正式徹回架，話就話要等立法會復會後再動議<br />\n到時建制派又玩反對，唔夠票一樣都係撤回唔到！！！<br />\n<br />\n10月1號之後先復會，過晒國慶采你都有味呀！<br />\n<br />\n佢既目的係降溫去應付兩件事：<br />\n1. 美國國會既香港關係法<br />\n2. 十月一中共国慶<br />\n<br />\n到復會前既時間仲可以清算所有示威過/鬧過警察既人，一石三鳥<br />\n<br />\n一定要傳出去比無聽既人知道！！！！<br />\n五大訴求、缺一不可！！！！<br />\n光復香港、時代革命！！！！"},{"pid":"ae296add8191e2e1fca926f16b4f969396b4673f","tid":1540600,"uid":29319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:56:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e0ac9296794c7567cd5582e2ab1ebb9f8d4978a1","tid":1540600,"uid":29319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:57:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"00f5e5e70d246b003a4fa704f1c8a3fe94ff68f7","tid":1540600,"uid":29319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:57:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d143eae4619a20ec0a6b9189d04f961e51df55f4","tid":1540600,"uid":287594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:57:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QUGSMa3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQUGSMa3.gif&h=1c74332a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【長期抗爭】最簡單有效嘅日常抗爭<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538155\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538155</a>"},{"pid":"c12ef83d5bf0f44c28f92021f379df37eb4152c4","tid":1540600,"uid":51618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:57:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b99fee9eaf9dc090377228b98d3d2f51723fc113","